Fast Company: “Why The Military And Corporate America Want To Make AI Explain Itself” (Singh quoted)
June 23, 2017 “If you go to a doctor and the doctor says, ‘Hey, you have six months to live,’ and offers absolutely no explanation as to why the doctor is saying that, that would be a pretty poor doctor,” says Sameer Singh, an assistant professor of computer science at the University of California at Irvine.
Read the full story at Fast Company.
